# Vasiliy Didukh | 3D Architectural Portfolio

🎨 Welcome to my official online portfolio showcasing selected works in 3D architectural visualization.

## 🖼️ Live Demo
**View the live portfolio:**  
➡️ [https://snejunka.github.io/vasiliy-portfolio/](https://snejunka.github.io/vasiliy-portfolio/)

## 📂 Contents
- `index.html` — Main portfolio page
- `renders/` — Gallery of 3D renders
- `Vasiliy_Didukh_Portfolio_Optimized.pdf` — Downloadable portfolio PDF

## 🌟 Features
- Minimalist dark/light theme switcher
- Preload spinner while gallery loads
- Responsive grid layout for all devices
- Easy download link for portfolio PDF
- Designed to be clean, fast, and elegant

## ⚙️ Technologies
- HTML5 + CSS3 (Vanilla)
- Responsive design with grid layout
- JavaScript for theme toggle and loader

